<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background">1. Data Collection</h2>
<p>At TinyTots, we prioritize the privacy and security of your family's information. We collect data necessary to provide our refined nursery services and process your orders efficiently. This includes personal identification information, browsing behavior, and purchase history.</p>
<p>The information we collect is utilized strictly for improving your experience, tailoring our recommendations, and ensuring seamless service delivery. We do not sell your personal data to third parties. For a comprehensive breakdown of our data handling practices, please review our detailed <a class="underline decoration-surface-dim hover:text-[#7FA8C9] hover:decoration-[#7FA8C9] transition-colors" href="#">Information Security Guidelines</a>.</p>
