<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background">5. Governing Law</h2>
<p>These Terms of Service and any separate agreements whereby we provide you services shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which TinyTots operates.</p>
